title: Voting for our next purchases
body:
BEFORE MAKING YOUR VOTE YOU MUST READ KAIJU RECENT ROADMAP UPDATE AND COOL CATS ROADMAP UPDATE

We can buy 3 kaijus, we can buy 2 Cool Cats, we can buy 1 Kaiju and 1 Cool cat, we can also buy MAYC or other smaller projects. We can also wait until we have more funds to buy other projects from our next royalty cut.

-Pros of buying now with our funds: Can lead to a volume increase, higher staking percentage, higher floor, added value to the Zombiez DAO. 

-Pros of buying 3 Kaijus: High upside/could be a very low-risk play considering their team and $RWASTE. We can enter the top 5 Kaiju holders and become the DAO that owns most of their project. This could have a massive influence in the project's future as we can make a ton of decisions. This can also make a massive statement as we continue to accumulate and people continue to invest in zombiez due to having more and more Kaijus inside the vault.
-Cons of buying 3 kaijus: We won't have other nfts in vault for now, until we can diversify later with our next royalty check. 

-Pros of buying 2 Cool cats: Can lead to more exposure to newer investors, we can be seen as diversifying and expanding our vault, bluechip project with lower risk, stable floor
-Cons of buying 2 Cool Cats: Some people may be weary of the project as they like the idea of a Kaiju focused DAO until we have a stronger base of Kaijus. Cool cats has been stable at the current floor price and dipping down and has not come out with anything crazy in their recent roadmap. There is another DAO that owns over 15+ cool cats, we would only be buying 2, and this might be considered a negative in some people's eyes as people may look at it as we are copying others. 

We can also buy Kaijus and cool cats, by doing 1 CC and 1 Kaiju with current funds until next payout.
